<div class='row'>
  <div class='jumbotron jumbotron-fluid col-md-12'>
    <div class='container'>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="loader_holder col-lg-12 hidden">
          <div class="loader"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <h1 style='text-align: center;'>MAAP User Shared Data Questionnaire</h1>
      <div class="bs-stepper">
        <div class="bs-stepper-header" role="tablist">
          <div class="step" data-target="#collection_info">
            <button type="button" class="step-trigger" role="tab" aria-controls="collection_info" id="collection_info_trigger" disabled>
              <span class="bs-stepper-circle">1</span>
              <span class="bs-stepper-label">Collection Information</span>
            </button>
          </div>
          <div class="line"></div>
          <div class="step" data-target="#data_info">
            <button type="button" class="step-trigger" role="tab" aria-controls="data-info" id="data_info_trigger" disabled>
              <span class="bs-stepper-circle">2</span>
              <span class="bs-stepper-label">Data Information</span>
            </button>
          </div>
          <div class="line"></div>
          <div class="step" data-target="#related_info">
            <button type="button" class="step-trigger" role="tab" aria-controls="related_info" id="related_info_trigger" disabled>
              <span class="bs-stepper-circle">3</span>
              <span class="bs-stepper-label">Related URLs</span>
            </button>
          </div>
          <div class="line"></div>
          <div class="step" data-target="#keywords">
            <button type="button" class="step-trigger" role="tab" aria-controls="keywords" id="keywords_trigger" disabled>
              <span class="bs-stepper-circle">4</span>
              <span class="bs-stepper-label">Keywords</span>
            </button>
          </div>
          <div class="line"></div>
          <div class="step" data-target="#temporal_extent">
            <button type="button" class="step-trigger" role="tab" aria-controls="temporal_extent" id="temporal_extent_trigger" disabled>
              <span class="bs-stepper-circle">5</span>
              <span class="bs-stepper-label">Temporal Extent</span>
            </button>
          </div>
          <div class="line"></div>
          <div class="step" data-target="#spatial_extent">
            <button type="button" class="step-trigger" role="tab" aria-controls="spatial_extent" id="spatial_extent_trigger" disabled>
              <span class="bs-stepper-circle">6</span>
              <span class="bs-stepper-label">Spatial Extent</span>
            </button>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <hr/>
      <div class="details_holder <%= 'hidden' if @hide_form %>">
        <p>
          Thank you for sharing your data with the MAAP community! As a reminder, data shared through this process should be provided by you. You are responsible for any content you upload to the MAAP and please do not post content that isnâ€™t your own.
        </p>
        <p>
          Before the data can be ingested into the MAAP, we need to collect some information in order to both create metadata for the dataset and to aid in ingesting the data. <b>Note that once you start filling in the questionnaire, a unique identifier will be created for each dataset that you share. You can save this identifier and return to your work in the questionnaire as needed.</b>
        </p>
        <p>
          Asterisks in the questionnaire indicate required questions. Please note that the more information provided, the more complete the metadata will be and the easier it will be for other users to find your data in the MAAP.
        </p>
        <p>
          Best practices on sharing data including how to name and format your data can be found in the MAAP user documentation. 
        </p>
        <p>
          If you have any questions about the questionnaire, please contact the 
          <a href="mailto:ak0033@uah.edu">MAAP data team</a>.
        </p>
        <hr/>
        <div class='form-row' align='center'>
          <div class='form-group col-md-5'>
            <button class='button button-green btn btn-lg btn-success btn_start float-right' align='center'>
              Start New
            </button>
          </div>
          <div class='form-group col-md-1'>
            <p style='margin-top:1em;'>
              OR
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class='form-group col-md-5'>
            <button class='button btn btn-lg btn-primary btn_edit float-left' align='center'>
              Edit existing
            </button>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="form_holder <%= 'hidden' if not(@hide_form) %>">
        <%= render @partial, questionnaire: @questionnaire, current_resource: @current_resource, previous_partial: @previous_partial %>
      </div>
      <div class="edit_holder hidden">
        <div class='form-row'>
          <div class='form-group col-md-6'>
            <label>
              Unique Identifier:*
            </label>
            <input type="text" name="questionnaire_uuid" class='questionnaire_uuid' required></input>
          </div>
          <div class='form-group'>
            <div class='col-md-12'>
              <button class='button btn btn-primary btn-sm float-right btn_find disabled' disabled> Find Record </button>
              <button class='button btn btn-danger btn-sm btn_back'> Go Back </button>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class='form-group col-md-1 hidden'>
            <btn class='button btn btn-danger btn-sm btn_clone'> Clone </btn>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
